               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I was looking at Richardson's show; there was a crush of people, and I saw a boy taking the cigar-case out of the gentleman's pocket; the officers caught bold of him and took it from him; lie ran away, and the officer got bold of me.</p>
